00192 void ArrayAttributesTest::testproperty_Attributes()
00193 {
00194         ArrayAttributes atts;
00195         ParameterNameValuePairVector &params = atts.Attributes();
00196         ParameterNameValuePair param;
00197 
00198         param.Name = L"array-att-name-1";
00199         param.Value = L"array-att-value-1";
00200         params.push_back(param);
00201 
00202         param.Name = L"array-att-name-2";
00203         param.Value = L"array-att-value-2";
00204         params.push_back(param);
00205 
00206         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( params.size() == 2 );
00207 
00208         ParameterNameValuePairVector::iterator it = atts.Attributes().begin();
00209         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00210         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00211         ++it;
00212         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
00213         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-2" );
00214         ++it;
00215         CPPUNIT_ASSERT (it == atts.Attributes().end() );
00216 
00217         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[0].Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00218         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[0].Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00219         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[1].Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
00220         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( atts.Attributes()[1].Value == L"array-att-value-2" );
00221 }
